        <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">1. What ArcadeBloom is</h2>
            <p>ArcadeBloom is a directory. We publish reviews, how-to-play guides, and metadata about browser games, and we link to the original authors' sites where those games can be played. We do not host the games themselves.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">2. External links</h2>
            <p>Every "Play" action on ArcadeBloom sends you to a third-party site we do not control. Once you leave ArcadeBloom, the destination site's own terms and policies apply. We are not responsible for the content or behaviour of third-party sites.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">3. Reviews and content</h2>
            <p>Our reviews and guides are editorial opinion. We strive for accuracy but make no warranty about completeness. Game names, screenshots and other trademarks belong to their respective owners and are used here for identification and review purposes.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">4. Source attribution</h2>
            <p>Every catalogue entry records its author, source URL, and licence. If you believe an entry is inaccurately attributed, or if you are an author who wants a game delisted, see the <a href="/contact/" class="underline hover:text-white">contact page</a>.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">5. Changes to these terms</h2>
            <p>We may update these terms as the site evolves. Material changes will be reflected in the "last updated" date above.</p>
        </section>
